• Profile service startup sequences to identify performance bottlenecks
• Validate timing requirements (e.g., service must start within 30 seconds)
• Correlate events across multiple log files in chronological order
• Measure duration of operations with start/stop pattern pairs
• Analyze system startup or shutdown sequences and timing
• Track time between specific events across all nodes in a collect bundle

QUICK START EXAMPLE:

    # Create a simple model file (boot_timing.yaml):
    blocks:
