KEY FEATURES:
• No pattern matching: Collects every timestamped line in the window
• Recursive subdirectory discovery: Finds logs in nova/, sysinv/, ceph/, etc.
• Auto time detection: Defaults to 5 minutes before latest log
• Smart file filtering: Skips binary, non-log, ignored, and out-of-range files
